    <item>
      <title>安瓦尔（Anwar）否认马来西亚通过投资释放萨普拉能源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/anwar-denies-malaysia-bailing-out-sapura-energy-with-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣（Anwar Ibrahim）表示，他已下令对Sapura Energy Bhd。进行审计，并进行了管理的变更，然后批准了有争议的11亿林吉特（2.482亿美元）注入现金短缺的石油和天然气公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/anwar-denies-malaysia-bailing-out-sapura-energy-with-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 02:18:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
